{"tid":2334990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣深珠等多市無預警停水停電斷網 發改委官員：限電為達成減碳目標","createTime":"2020-12-21T13:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T19:25:45.000Z","uid":50386,"like":236,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6b18ebe47bf2f371baf141f35367154a56f0bf","tid":2334990,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"浙江、江西、湖南三省限電，引發強烈民怨和缺電質疑。國家發改委秘書長趙辰昕21日稱，浙江不存在缺電情況，<span class=\"red\">而是「個別地方」為促進節能減碳而採取限電措施。</span>趙辰昕堅稱，截至目前，中國電力供應「總體保持了平穩有序」，包括湖南、江西、浙江等省在內，「居民生活用電都沒有受到影響」；而用電量激增帶動煤炭需求增加，導致最近煤價「略微有些上漲」。發改委監測電廠存煤，無論存煤天數還是存煤總量「都是有保障的」。<br />\n<br />\n趙辰昕指出，相較於湖南、江西的電力缺口，浙江的情況和湖南、江西「還不完全一樣」，浙江電力供應「是能夠保障全省電力需求的，不存在電力供應不足的情況」。<span class=\"red\">（浙江）省內個別地方為了促進「節能減排（碳）」，採取了「限制電力消費」的一些措施。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/DFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FDFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=49415caa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FDFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY%2F&h=b50a1ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/DFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY/</a><br />\n<br />\n遲啲饑荒都係為達成營養目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fc6384a8e2e1109a63673cd889d73b8703d03f","tid":2334990,"uid":79117,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e25d26208d240a98886b902ada9d996697b93689","tid":2334990,"uid":386543,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a356eca34aa55b83a9fca27ccac1df6edb3e35","tid":2334990,"uid":279326,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:36:0