4,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"個目標我覺得未夠，可以做得更好，<br />\n<br />\n最好一，三，五，日停電<br />\n<br />\n二，四，六停水"},{"pid":"d0f195a88aa80728d77571ed132e938514378894","tid":2334990,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"支那為環保貢獻眾多，先釋出武漢肺炎，再限電減少二氧化碳排放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228c8d4dee39beeaca79cafcece1694533691162","tid":2334990,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5e6b18ebe47bf2f371baf141f35367154a56f0bf","tid":2334990,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"浙江、江西、湖南三省限電，引發強烈民怨和缺電質疑。國家發改委秘書長趙辰昕21日稱，浙江不存在缺電情況，<span class=\"red\">而是「個別地方」為促進節能減碳而採取限電措施。</span>趙辰昕堅稱，截至目前，中國電力供應「總體保持了平穩有序」，包括湖南、江西、浙江等省在內，「居民生活用電都沒有受到影響」；而用電量激增帶動煤炭需求增加，導致最近煤價「略微有些上漲」。發改委監測電廠存煤，無論存煤天數還是存煤總量「都是有保障的」。<br />\n<br />\n趙辰昕指出，相較於湖南、江西的電力缺口，浙江的情況和湖南、江西「還不完全一樣」，浙江電力供應「是能夠保障全省電力需求的，不存在電力供應不足的情況」。<span class=\"red\">（浙江）省內個別地方為了促進「節能減排（碳）」，採取了「限制電力消費」的一些措施。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/DFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FDFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=49415caa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201221%2FDFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY%2F&h=b50a1ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201221/DFOWAVAG5RDHNMJ7F3IYCFUSCY/</a><br />\n<br />\n遲啲饑荒都係為達成營養目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"一直都係咁宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61ptFtV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61ptFtV.jpg&h=1b56308a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f34249efa6819dff9443725024b3c40ff86b7e8","tid":2334990,"uid":3508